# COMMITS & DOCS

- Use Conventional Commits (feat, fix, docs, refactor, chore, test).
- After meaningful changes, update:
  - PLAN.md (next 3 tasks)
  - DECISIONS.log (what/why, date)
  - ARCH.md (if architecture changed)
- Keep README short with "Getting Started", "Run", "Test", and "Env vars".
